tool_arguments.code:
search_results = duckduckgo_search_results("who bought DLF Camelia apartments", 5)
import re
names = re.findall(r'(Anmol Singh Jaggi|Puneet Singh Jaggi|Deep Kalra|Sameer Manchanda|Ashish Gurnan|Rishi Parti)', str(search_results))
result = f"The following individuals bought apartments in DLF Camellias: {', '.join(names) if names else 'No names found in the search results.'}"
return result
